      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL SAKI (1) raced close the lead throughout and copped a check in the run, finishing a 3.5 lengths second (22.32) in a Grade 6 at this track. Tough to beat on best. TAKEOVER TARGET (4) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (21.70) at this track in a Grade 6. Has first look at box 4 this time. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. TOBIAS IVY (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 22.33 beating Federal Arlo. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Has definite claims. NEYTIRI MAGIC (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
